                             The PC PEDALS(TM)
                           Ordering Information

The PC Pedals is now being sold directly from IDD.  The retail price for
the PC Pedals is $219.95.  For a limited time InterACTIVE Digital Devices
is pre-selling the first 100 units with a $25.00 discount for a total of
$194.95, which includes shipping and handling.

To order products from IDD, send personal check, certified check, or
money order for the items wanted plus shipping and handling cost from
the chart in the ORDER INFO file.  COD orders are welcome.  For multiple
items, please call to get the exact shipping cost.  Georgia residents should
add 6.5% sales tax.

Please include the items wanted along with your name, telephone
number, and shipping address for immediate delivery.  If possible, include
your computer model, version of operating system, and software that you
will be using in conjunction with the products.

NOTE:  All dollar values mentioned in this information pack is in U.S.
dollars.  All purchases must be made in US dollars using the current
exchange rate.

Any orders recieved before November 20,1993 may have delivery delayed due to
production scheduling.
